name: Space Wolves II
blurb: Help us launch Space Wolves II on iOS. The popular puzzler that's been hailed as a cross between Angry Birds and Cut the Rope returns.

rewards.reward: Our sincere thanks for your good wishes. Every pledge is a source of encouragement to us and gratefully received. Thank you.
EARLY BIRD PLEDGE! Get the regular \u00a310 reward (THE GAME) for only \u00a35. Limited to the first 100.

THANKS! A big thank you from everyone at launch control! You have officially helped fund a Space Mission. Your name will appear on the \u201cWe made it happen\u201d page on the official Spaces Wolves 2 website.
EARLY BIRD PLEDGE! Limited to the first 500. You will receive all the rewards from the \u00a315 pledge for only \u00a310!

THE GAME - You will receive a copy of the game including all additional planets achieved with stretch goals and your name will appear on the \u201cWe made it happen\u201d page on the official SW website.

HD ARTWORK - You will receive an exclusive HD resolution digital poster of Royston and the Space Wolves.  You will also receive a copy of the game  (including extra stretch goal planets) and your name will appear on the \u201cWe made it happen\u201d page on the official SW website.

PERSONALISED HD ARTWORK - You will receive a HD resolution digital poster featuring a personalised message from Royston, the Space Wolves and the ground crew. You will receive a copy of the game and your name will appear on the \u201cWe made it happen\u201d page on the official SW website.

FRIENDS WITH THE STARS - Royston will post a personal thank you message to you on his Facebook page, so that all your friends can see that you hang out with Space explorers and help fund their missions to Outer Space. You also get the game, the artwork and the thank you.

BETA TESTER - EARLY BIRD! You will become an official beta tester. You will receive the game before anyone else on earth and can also give us your feedback. You also get the finished game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you. Please note:  Beta testers will need iPhone running iOS 5.0 or later. This reward is not available with the higher value rewards.

EXCLUSIVE CREW T-SHIRT - An exclusive limited edition Space Wolves \u201cCREW\u201d T-shirt, featuring original artwork from the Space Wolves game. You also get the game, the facebook message, the artwork and your name credited on the website.

NAME A SPACE WOLF - One of the Space Wolves will be given your choice of name. It can even be your name or a friend's name. As long as it's not offensive, or a website address, or a trademark name that you don't own the rights to. You will receive a HD digital certificate of your named Space Wolf. You also get the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you.

CREDIT WHERE IT'S DUE - An in-game name credit. You will appear on the credits page in the game as a special thanks. You also get to name a Space Wolf (see above), a copy of the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you.

SIGNED FRAMED ARTWORK - A signed framed A4 picture of Royston and the Space Wolves with a personalized thank you message. You also get an in-game credit, name a Space Wolf (see above), a copy of the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you.

EXCLUSIVE ANIMATED GIF - A world exclusive specially created animated gif of Royston saying thank you for making him happen. You also get the signed framed picture, an in-game credit, name a Space Wolf (see above), a copy of the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you.
EARLY BIG BIRD REWARD! Get all the \u00a33000 rewards for only \u00a32000.

PERSONALISED ANIMATION - A 20 second Space Wolves animation video with personalised dialogue voiced by Royston Starkey and the Space Wolves. You also get the animated gif, the signed framed picture, an in-game credit, name a Space Wolf, a copy of the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you. NOTE: Message must not be offensive/illegal/promotional.

THE MOTHERSHIP OF REWARDS ... MARRIAGE. For one lucky person we can arrange it for Royston and the Space Wolves quartet to propose to your better half. The personalised video can then be emailed or posted online. You also get the animated gif, the signed framed picture, an in-game credit, name a Space Wolf, a copy of the game, the facebook message, the artwork and the thank you. We can not guarantee that they will say yes, but if they do we'll let as many people know as possible. Good luck!
